    code: "#include <iostream>\nusing namespace std;\n\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    // A power of two has exactly one bit set: n & (n-1) clears that bit.\n    // The result is 0 iff n was a power of two; guard n > 0 to exclude 0/negatives.\n    bool isPowerOfTwo(int n) {\n        return n > 0 && (n & (n - 1)) == 0;\n    }\n};",
